6
00:00:38,253 --> 00:00:40,642
- Good morning.
- Morning.

7
00:00:40,853 --> 00:00:44,289
- State your name for the record.
- Daniel Ocean.

8
00:00:44,613 --> 00:00:48,288
Thank you. The purpose of this
hearing is to determine...

9
00:00:48,493 --> 00:00:51,485
...whether you are
likely to break the law again.

10
00:00:51,693 --> 00:00:55,971
This was your first conviction,
but you've been implicated...

11
00:00:56,173 --> 00:00:58,971
...in a dozen other schemes
and frauds.

12
00:00:59,173 --> 00:01:01,607
What can you tell us about this?

13
00:01:02,453 --> 00:01:05,251
As you say, ma'am,
I was never charged.

14
00:01:05,973 --> 00:01:08,203
We're trying to find out...

15
00:01:08,413 --> 00:01:11,211
...if there was a reason
for committing this crime...

16
00:01:11,413 --> 00:01:14,246
...or just a reason
you got caught this time.

17
00:01:14,453 --> 00:01:19,129
My wife left me. I was upset.
I got into a self-destructive pattern.

18
00:01:20,373 --> 00:01:24,685
If released, is it likely you'd fall
back into a similar pattern?

19
00:01:24,893 --> 00:01:29,250
She left me once. I doubt
she'd do it again just for kicks.

20
00:01:29,453 --> 00:01:34,891
Mr. Ocean, what do you think
you would do if released?

21
00:02:55,133 --> 00:02:56,851
- Chips, please.
- Sure.

22
00:02:59,413 --> 00:03:03,042
- Change 150. Quarters or nickels?
- Quarters are fine.

23
00:03:05,893 --> 00:03:08,282
- Good luck.
- Thank you.

24
00:03:14,453 --> 00:03:18,605
20. Dealer has 19.
Good start.

25
00:03:22,733 --> 00:03:26,123
- I'm going on break now.
- Here. Thank you very much.

26
00:03:27,413 --> 00:03:30,086
- Good luck.
- You have a good one.

27
00:03:30,973 --> 00:03:33,771
- How are you, sir?
- Hello, Frank.

28
00:03:37,413 --> 00:03:42,043
I beg your pardon. You must have me
confused with someone else.

29
00:03:42,253 --> 00:03:45,882
My name is Ramón.
As you can see right here.

30
00:03:49,253 --> 00:03:51,847
- My mistake.
- No problem, sir.

31
00:03:52,213 --> 00:03:54,647
The table's cold anyway.

32
00:03:54,853 --> 00:03:59,210
You might want to try the lounge
at Caesars. Gets busy after 1:00.

33
00:03:59,413 --> 00:04:01,165
- 1:00?
