34
00:04:02,013 --> 00:04:03,731
Thanks, Ramón.

35
00:04:05,133 --> 00:04:06,361
Thank you.

36
00:04:15,253 --> 00:04:19,212
- Checking up on current events?
- Ramón?

37
00:04:19,413 --> 00:04:24,168
Glad to meet you. Frank Catton
can't get past the gaming board.

38
00:04:24,373 --> 00:04:26,682
- You just got out?
- This afternoon.

39
00:04:27,173 --> 00:04:28,208
You seen him?

40
00:04:28,613 --> 00:04:33,323
I heard he was teaching movie stars
how to play cards. Why?

41
00:04:33,973 --> 00:04:35,565
You have a plan already?

42
00:04:35,893 --> 00:04:38,885
Are you kidding?
I just became a citizen again.

43
00:04:39,093 --> 00:04:40,367
Officer Brooks...

44
00:04:40,733 --> 00:04:45,124
...this is Danny Ocean. I was told
to contact you within 24 hours.

45
00:04:46,013 --> 00:04:49,164
No, sir, I haven't
been getting in trouble.

46
00:04:50,133 --> 00:04:53,125
No, sir, I haven't been drinking.

47
00:04:53,333 --> 00:04:56,450
No, sir, I wouldn't even think
