Two cards.

96
00:08:19,173 --> 00:08:21,607
I just got out of prison.

97
00:08:23,173 --> 00:08:26,131
- Really?
- Why were you in prison?

98
00:08:26,733 --> 00:08:28,644
I stole things.

99
