with the guy.

213
00:15:56,733 --> 00:15:59,088
- Our pleasure.
- I'd never been to Belize.

214
00:15:59,293 --> 00:16:04,048
Give Dominic your addresses.
I got some furniture to send you.

215
00:16:05,173 --> 00:16:10,850
Just out of curiosity, which casinos
did you geniuses pick to rob?

216
00:16:12,053 --> 00:16:15,250
The Bellagio, the Mirage
and the MGM Grand.

217
00:16:17,133 --> 00:16:20,330
Those are Terry Benedict's casinos.

218
00:16:20,533 --> 00:16:22,808
- Is that right?
- That's right.

219
00:16:23,573 --> 00:16:25,370
You guys...

220
00:16:26,453 --> 00:16:29,092
...what do you got against
Terry Benedict?

221
00:16:29,333 --> 00:16:32,803
What do you have against him?
That's the question.

222
00:16:33,013 --> 00:16:37,564
He torpedoed my casino.
Muscled me out.

223
00:16:37,773 --> 00:16:42,893
Now he's gonna blow it up next month
to make way for some monstrosity.

224
00:16:43,213 --> 00:16:46,603
- I see what you're doing.
- What are we doing?

225
00:16:47,773 --> 00:16:52,289
If you're gonna steal from Terry
Benedict, you better goddamn know.

226
00:16:52,533 --> 00:16:56,446
This used to be civilized.
You'd hit a guy, he'd whack you.

227
00:16:56,693 --> 00:16:58,445
But Benedict... .

228
00:16:59,413 --> 00:17:03,122
At the end of it, he'd better not
know you're involved.

229
00:17:03,333 --> 00:17:07,963
Because he'll kill you,
then he'll go to work on you.

230
00:17:08,893 --> 00:17:12,283
That's why we have to be
very careful, very precise.

231
00:17:12,533 --> 00:17:13,852
Well-funded.

232
00:17:14,773 --> 00:17:16,843
You gotta be nuts, too.

233
00:17:17,173 --> 00:17:21,166
