252
00:19:15,413 --> 00:19:17,847
Hey, RadioShack. Relax.

253
00:19:27,413 --> 00:19:28,448
Munitions.

254
00:19:28,733 --> 00:19:30,610
- Phil Turrentine.
- Dead.

255
00:19:31,053 --> 00:19:33,169
