262
00:20:14,973 --> 00:20:18,283
You tossers!
You had one job to do!

263
00:20:22,493 --> 00:20:24,609
That's all you used in the event?

264
00:20:24,933 --> 00:20:28,005
- You accusing me of booby-trapping?
