265
00:20:28,213 --> 00:20:32,206
Booby traps aren't Mr. Tarr's style.
Isn't that right?

266
00:20:32,693 --> 00:20:34,092
Basher?

267
00:20:34,413 --> 00:20:36,369
Peck. ATF.

268
00:20:36,853 --> 00:20:38,332
Let me venture a guess.

269
00:20:38,573 --> 00:20:43,772
Simple G-4 mainliner, back wound,
quick fuse with a drag under 20 feet.

270
00:20:44,373 --> 00:20:47,251
Let me ask you this.
You search this scumbag...

271
00:20:47,573 --> 00:20:50,451
...for booby traps?
I mean, really searched.

272
00:20:50,813 --> 00:20:52,132
Stand back.

273
00:20:52,453 --> 00:20:53,932
Here we go.

274
00:20:54,333 --> 00:20:56,608
- Find Griggs. I need him.
- Who?

275
00:20:56,973 --> 00:20:58,691
Just find him, will you?

276
00:21:00,133 --> 00:21:03,523
Can you put something together
with what I gave you?

277
00:21:03,773 --> 00:21:04,888
Done.

278
00:21:06,373 --> 00:21:09,251
- Is Danny about?
- He's around the corner.

279
00:21:09,453 --> 00:21:13,241
Terrific. It'll be nice working
with proper villains again.

280
00:21:13,693 --> 00:21:15,763
Everybody down! Get down!

281
00:21:17,613 --> 00:21:19,922
They weren't expecting that shit!

282
00:21:20,293 --> 00:21:21,806
- Nice work.
- Thanks.

283
00:21:39,893 --> 00:21:43,932
- Which one's the Amazing Yen?
- The little Chinese guy.

284
00:21:48,213 --> 00:21:51,125
- Who else is on the list?
- He is the list.

285
00:21:55,253 --> 00:21:57,483
It doesn't seem that diff...

286
00:22:06,453 --> 00:22:10,366
- We got a grease man.
- We got a grease man.

