- He get religion?

289
00:22:19,573 --> 00:22:21,291
Ulcers.

290
00:22:23,413 --> 00:22:26,325
- You could ask him.
- Hey, I could ask him.

291
00:22:53,013 --> 00:22:55,891
I saw you at the paddock...

292
00:22:56,213 --> 00:23:01,003
...before the second race, outside
the men's room when I placed my bet.

293
00:23:02,253 --> 00:23:05,211
I saw you before you even
got up this morning.

294
00:23:05,693 --> 00:23:08,685
- How you been, Saul?
- Never better.

295
00:23:08,933 --> 00:23:10,730
What's with the orange?

296
00:23:10,933 --> 00:23:15,324
- My doctor says I need vitamins.
- Why don't you take vitamins?

297
00:23:15,693 --> 00:23:18,048
