- They say taupe is very soothing.

428
00:36:06,093 --> 00:36:08,209
- Hi.
- Fine, thanks.

429
00:36:19,373 --> 00:36:21,409
- Move the balloons.
- Move them?

430
00:36:21,613 --> 00:36:23,569
I have a client waiting for these.

431
00:36:23,773 --> 00:36:29,086
I don't have time to fool around
with you circus animals.

432
00:37:01,253 --> 00:37:03,528
Hey! Hold up a minute!

433
00:37:04,293 --> 00:37:05,851
Excuse me!

434
00:37:06,053 --> 00:37:08,931
Hey! Excuse me!

435
00:37:09,173 --> 00:37:14,372
- Hey, you dropped this.
- Oh, thank you.

436
00:37:14,573 --> 00:37:17,770
- How's the reception on those things?
- Excellent.

437
00:37:18,293 --> 00:37:21,251
- Take care.
- Thanks.

438
00:37:27,333 --> 00:37:29,847
- Well... .
- Yeah.

439
00:37:31,933 --> 00:37:33,446
Fourth task: construction.

440
00:37:33,693 --> 00:37:37,049
We need to build an exact
replica of the Bellagio vault.

441
00:37:37,213 --> 00:37:40,603
- To practice?
- Something like that.

442
00:37:41,093 --> 00:37:42,731
Fifth task: intelligence.

443
00:37:42,933 --> 00:37:46,767
We need those codes, Linus,
from the guy who has all three.

444
00:37:46,973 --> 00:37:50,170
- Who, Benedict?
- Learn to love his shadow.

445
00:37:50,373 --> 00:37:54,889
- All I get to do is watch the guy?
- Gotta walk before you crawl.

446
00:37:55,333 --> 00:37:58,564
- Reverse that.
- Sixth task: transport.

447
00:38:02,533 --> 00:38:07,527
Well, I am sorry, but $ 18,500 a piece
is the best offer that I can make.

448
00:38:08,453 --> 00:38:10,364
Well, I understand.

449
00:38:10,733 --> 00:38:15,329
- They are some great-looking vans.
